OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FMore than 9 million pounds will be
OL,8,Foffered in compensation to Southern
OL,9,FWater customers after disruption to
OL,10,Fthe water supply this week in parts of
OL,11,FHampshire.
OL,13,FAround 58,000 properties in
OL,14,FSouthampton, Romsey, Eastleigh and the
OL,15,FNew Forest were affected following
OL,16,Fissues at the company's Testwood Water
OL,17,Fsite on Wednesday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/15
