OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FThousands of people had to rely on
OL,8,Fbottled water stations, at Places
OL,9,FLeisure Centre in Eastleigh,
OL,10,FStaplewood Football Development Centre
OL,11,Fand Calshot Road Car Park.
OL,13,FFive schools in Southampton and four
OL,14,Fin the New Forest and Test Valley had
OL,15,Fto close due to the lack of water.
OL,17,FSouthampton General Hospital had 7
OL,18,Ftankers dedicated to supplying water
OL,19,Fto the site, so it could continue to
OL,20,Ftreat patients.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/15
