OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FSouthern Water's Chief Executive,
OL,8,FLawrence Gosden, has apologised for
OL,9,Fwhat he calls the biggest water supply
OL,10,Fincident in the company's history and
OL,11,Fhas promised to review the incident.
OL,13,FIn a statement issued on Friday
OL,14,Fevening, the firm said it will be
OL,15,Foffering homes and businesses
OL,16,Fcompensation for the loss of supply
OL,17,Fthey had to put up with.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/15
