OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FAll customers will hear from Southern
OL,8,FWater in writing in the next three
OL,9,Fweeks what compensation they will
OL,10,Freceive.
OL,12,FThe company says it will apply
OL,13,Fcompensation at the new rates proposed
OL,14,Fby the Government and being brought
OL,15,Fbefore Parliament in the New Year.
OL,17,FSouthern Water says the approximate
OL,18,Fcost of paying this compensation will
OL,19,Fbe #9.7 million.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/15
