OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,FThe firm has also promised to invest a
OL,8,Fquarter of a billion pounds to improve
OL,9,Fthe Testwood Water site, which serves
OL,10,Fjust over 70,000 homes and businesses.
OL,12,FIn a statement, Southern Water's Chief
OL,13,FExecutive, Lawrence Gosden said: "I
OL,14,Fwant to apologise personally to the
OL,15,Fcommunity in Hampshire following the
OL,16,Fwater supply interruption this week,
OL,17,Ffor the huge disruption and
OL,18,Finconvenience it caused so many people
OL,19,Fso close to Christmas.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/15
