OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"In this note I also set out a
OL,8,Fcommitment to compensate customers,
OL,9,Fcosting #9.7 million, and I promise to
OL,10,Freview this incident thoroughly and
OL,11,Flearn the lessons.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/15
