OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"The community served by the Testwood
OL,8,Fwater works has suffered similar
OL,9,Finterruptions before, and so what
OL,10,Fhappened this week is a repeat for
OL,11,Fmany who live in the area. I
OL,12,Funderstand how disruptive and
OL,13,Finfuriating this was for all those
OL,14,Faffected, and I'm very sorry. It was
OL,15,Fthe single biggest water supply
OL,16,Fincident in our company's history.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/15
