OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"Testwood serves just over 70,000
OL,8,Fhomes and businesses, and the
OL,9,Fconsequences of its shutdown over a
OL,10,Ftechnical fault were widespread and
OL,11,Fextremely rapid. Hundreds of Southern
OL,12,FWater employees staff responded
OL,13,Fquickly, mobilising to fix the fault,
OL,14,Fvolunteering to staff bottled water
OL,15,Fstations, and working round the clock
OL,16,Fto keep the community informed. Many
OL,17,Fof them live in the local community or
OL,18,Fnearby in Hampshire. It was a huge
OL,19,Feffort.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
