PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1734786943
OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"With 58,000 properties left without
OL,8,Fwater, opening just one bottled water
OL,9,Fstation on the first day was far from
OL,10,Fadequate. We had a lot of willing
OL,11,Femployees ready to staff more
OL,12,Fstations, but we and our partners
OL,13,Ffailed to obtain sufficient quantities
OL,14,Fof bottled water. This left people
OL,15,Fqueuing for hours, in cars or on foot.
OL,16,FThis fell far short of what the
OL,17,Fcommunity needed.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/15
