OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1734786943
OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"In addition, our more vulnerable
OL,8,Fcustomers ` those on the Priority
OL,9,FServices Register ` were poorly
OL,10,Fserved, having to wait too long for
OL,11,Fdeliveries to arrive, and in some
OL,12,Fcases not receiving a delivery at all.
OL,13,FThere's always a degree of confusion
OL,14,Fover the PSR during an incident, as we
OL,15,Fmerge our lists with those of councils
OL,16,Fand the NHS, and people phone in to
OL,17,Flet us know that they or a relative
OL,18,Fare vulnerable. The list more than
OL,19,Ftripled inside a day to 20,000
OL,20,Fhouseholds. However that's no excuse.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
