OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1734786943
OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"I want to offer the community
OL,8,Faffected by this incident some
OL,9,Fassurances. Firstly, we will be
OL,10,Foffering our customers ` homes and
OL,11,Fbusinesses ` compensation for the loss
OL,12,Fof supply they had to put up with. All
OL,13,Fcustomers will hear from us in writing
OL,14,Fin the next three weeks what
OL,15,Fcompensation they will receive. We
OL,16,Fwill apply compensation at the new
OL,17,Frates proposed by the Government and
OL,18,Fbeing brought before Parliament in the
OL,19,FNew Year. Even though these may not
OL,20,Fcome into force in law until April, we
OL,21,Fwill use them as the standard. The
OL,22,Fapproximate cost to Southern Water of
OL,23,Fpaying this compensation will be #9.7
OL,24,Fmillion.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
