OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1734786943
OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"Secondly, I promise that we are going
OL,8,Fto review very thoroughly what went
OL,9,Fwrong in the Testwood incident, and
OL,10,Flearn the lessons. This includes
OL,11,Ftaking whatever steps are needed to
OL,12,Fensure that we are better prepared for
OL,13,Fsuch incidents in future. We'll be
OL,14,Fheld to account by your MPs and
OL,15,Felected councillors over the measures
OL,16,Fwe take.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
