OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1734786943
OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"Unfortunately, similar incidents
OL,8,Fcannot be ruled out across the region
OL,9,Fin future. The new management team at
OL,10,FSouthern Water is determined to
OL,11,Fdeliver improvements, and a turnaround
OL,12,Ffor the company. But we have a lot of
OL,13,Fageing infrastructure, like Testwood
OL,14,Fwater works, which needs to be
OL,15,Fmodernised or replaced. It should have
OL,16,Fbeen done a long time ago, but
OL,17,Finvestment was squeezed as customer
OL,18,Fbills remained static for more than a
OL,19,Fdecade. This badly needed investment
OL,20,Fis now coming, and is the main reason
OL,21,Fcustomer bills are going to rise
OL,22,Fsignificantly over the next 5 years.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/15
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
