OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F412A1734786943
OL,3,CSouthern Water customers will be
OL,4,Ccompensated #9.7 million after loss of
OL,5,Csupply
OL,7,F"At Testwood itself over the next 7
OL,8,Fyears, we're going to invest a quarter
OL,9,Fof a billion pounds on improving the
OL,10,Fsite for our customers. The money will
OL,11,Fbe spent on modern equipment, making
OL,12,FTestwood efficient and resilient - far
OL,13,Fless prone to failure.
OL,15,F"I would end by repeating once more my
OL,16,Fsincere apology to everyone for the
OL,17,Finconvenience and disruption caused by
OL,18,Fthis incident."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G15/15
